    "name": "Stray Birds Taichung Hostel",
    "detail": "Prior to this trip, I was so hesitant to make a booking in a hostel due to couple of bad experiences I had staying at a hostel. But due to alot of outstanding reviews and comments about this hostel, I have made a risks of booking and I have never been resentful about that decision. The place was so pleasant, clean and peaceful. it is located at the west district of taichung where a lot of good cafes and places sprawled. I also love the fact that it is near bus station. I love that the rooms are spacious and the bathroom is squeaky clean. You will not feel like your are sharing comfort room with others as there are good number of cubicles (both bathroom and comfort room). I also love their free breakfast. I will surely stay here should I return to Taichung. ",
